## 1. SYSTEM OVERVIEW

| Attribute | Value |
|-----------|-------|
| **Backend** | FastAPI (Python) + SQLAlchemy 2.0 (Mapped declarative) |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL 15+ with Row-Level Security (RLS) |
| **Auth** | JWT Bearer tokens (HS256), permission-based RBAC |
| **Tenancy** | Single-database multi-tenant via `app.tenant_id` GUC + RLS policies |
| **Architecture** | Transactional outbox (domain events), double-entry ledger, soft-delete everywhere |
| **Currency** | IQD (Iraqi Dinar) — all monetary values are **integer fils** (no floats) |

